Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.63,0:00:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR]\NWealth, fame, power...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.55,0:00:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Gold Roger, the King\Nof the Pirates,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.21,0:00:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,attained this and everything\Nelse the world had to offer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.01,0:00:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And his dying words drove\Ncountless souls to the seas.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.46,0:00:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[GOLD ROGER]\NYou want my treasure?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.04,0:00:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I left everything I gathered\Ntogether in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.55,0:00:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you just have to find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.71,0:00:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[NARRATOR] These words\Nlured men to the Grand Line
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.42,0:00:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,in pursuit of dreams greater\Nthan they've ever dared
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.59,0:00:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,to imagine! This is the time\Nknown as the Great Pirate Era!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.83,0:00:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.42,0:00:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.17,0:00:58.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}One Piece!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.42,0:01:08.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Compass left behind{\i0}\N{\i1}It'll only slow us down{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.88,0:01:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Your heart will be your guide{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.13,0:01:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Raise the sails{\i0}\N{\i1}and take the helm{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.51,0:01:20.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That legendary place that the{\i0}\N{\i1}end of the map reveals{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.13,0:01:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is only legendary{\i0}\N{\i1}until someone proves it real{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.88,0:01:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Through it all, through all{\i0}\N{\i1}the troubled times, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.88,0:01:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}through the heartache,{\i0}\N{\i1}and through the pain{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.59,0:01:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Know that I will be there{\i0}\N{\i1}to stand by you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.84,0:01:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just like I know{\i0}\N{\i1}you'll stand by me! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.34,0:01:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So come aboard and bring along{\i0}\N{\i1}all your hopes and dreams{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Together we will find everything{\i0}\N{\i1}that we're looking for{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.88,0:01:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's always room for you{\i0}\N{\i1}if you want to be my friend{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.84,0:02:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are, we are on the cruise{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.38,0:02:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We are!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.75,0:02:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Might as well throw\Nthat gas mask away!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.00,0:02:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You are no longer worthy\Nto be a Krieg Pirate.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.71,0:02:18.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NDie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.00,0:02:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.55,0:02:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] I'm not going to let\Nthat happen, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wasting your\Ntime, Chore Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:31.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yelping]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.26,0:02:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.01,0:02:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.42,0:02:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.71,0:02:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NAw, crap.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.51,0:02:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.79,0:02:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to\Nlisten to that blowhard,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.17,0:02:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,because I'm gonna\Nkick his ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.46,0:02:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.38,0:02:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No! My captain\Ncannot be defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don Krieg is the\Nstrongest man alive
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.67,0:03:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and I respect his punishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.88,0:03:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you please snap out of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.13,0:03:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I deserve it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Obeying my emotions meant\Nbetraying my captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.84,0:03:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were in his position, then\NI would've done the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.72,0:03:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, death is the\Nonly honor I have left.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.88,0:03:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.71,0:03:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI grunts]\NWhy? No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh! So you've\Nremembered your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.75,0:03:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But, it's much\Ntoo late for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.17,0:03:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, you will both die together.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.51,0:03:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the MH 5...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.13,0:03:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Poison...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.04,0:03:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Gas Bomb...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.17,0:03:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.22,0:03:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\N"I Won't Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.34,0:03:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Fierce Battle, Luffy vs. Krieg."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.05,0:03:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.47,0:03:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY]\NGet inside the restaurant!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.84,0:04:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,--[LUFFY] Thank you!\N--[PIRATES gasp]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Sanji, Ghin, catch!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.00,0:04:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, for mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.29,0:04:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]\NWhere'd they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.55,0:04:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.17,0:04:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.50,0:04:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[yelling]\NDon't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.05,0:04:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't die, don't die,\Ndon't die, don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.17,0:04:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.26,0:04:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NThis, is power.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.42,0:04:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY huffs]\NI'm alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.38,0:04:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That mask appeared just in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.75,0:05:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK J]\NWhat a crazy bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.71,0:05:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK K]\NHe tried to kill us all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.42,0:05:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy's gotta be insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.13,0:05:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK L] I can't believe\Nhe used poison gas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.34,0:05:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK JJ]\NHe must be a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.55,0:05:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No human would do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.01,0:05:13.47,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.63,0:05:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Do ya' think Sanji and\Nthe Chore Boy made it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.21,0:05:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, the poison\Ngas is clearing up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.34,0:05:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NGhin!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.79,0:05:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NLet go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.84,0:05:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You can let go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.76,0:05:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ghin, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.47,0:05:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN gasping]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:05:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your mask...\Nyou gave it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:00.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NNo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:03.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.97,0:06:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NWhat a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.58,0:06:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You are paying for a plate\Nof food with your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.92,0:06:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you'll learn...\Nwhen you're dead. Heh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.43,0:06:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.34,0:06:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That bastard.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.42,0:06:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,First he orders\NGhin to kill himself
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.42,0:06:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and then he mocks the poor guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,He should respect the fact\Nthat he followed his order
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.63,0:06:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.75,0:06:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[labored breathng]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.38,0:06:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Don Krieg!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.30,0:06:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghin...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.88,0:06:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN panting]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:52.05,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it seems...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don Krieg was not the right\Nman for you to follow, was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.75,0:07:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.55,0:07:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NIt figures
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.34,0:07:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that you still feel for\Nthat pathetic scum.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.63,0:07:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NScum?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.38,0:07:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NThat's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.54,0:07:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone who loses focus\Nand betrays my ship,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.29,0:07:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,is worthless to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.75,0:07:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll almost\Ncertainly do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.05,0:07:14.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Putting him out of his\Nmisery is an act of mercy
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.34,0:07:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,to keep him from dishonoring\Nhimself in the future
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.04,0:07:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and endangering my crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.75,0:07:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But... he just...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.38,0:07:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I never thought the Captain\Nwould kill his chief commander!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.43,0:07:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghin has been his right hand man
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,for even longer than I've\Nbeen part of the crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, see, no one's\Never showed more loyalty
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.42,0:07:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,to Don Krieg than Ghin\Nhas over the years.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.54,0:07:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,How could he forget what\NGhin did for us after
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.88,0:07:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,we escaped from the Grand Line
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.38,0:07:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and Fullbody's\NMarines were after us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.34,0:07:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It was a miracle we escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.97,0:07:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE J] Yeah, he was willing\Nto sacrifice his life for us
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.96,0:07:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,by acting as a decoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.50,0:07:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Without him, we wouldn't\Nhave made it out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ghin's laid down his\Nlife for Don Krieg
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,a hundred times, easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe the\Ncaptain would kill him
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.71,0:07:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,with such little care.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.04,0:07:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[panting, coughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.42,0:08:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so cruel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.92,0:08:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Patty, get the kit, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.42,0:08:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for food poisoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think it will\Nwork on gas, Sanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.38,0:08:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care! We have to try!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.30,0:08:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Put the mask on em'.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.59,0:08:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It will detoxify the\Ngas in his lungs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, bring him upstairs\Nand let him breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.67,0:08:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the only chance\Nwe have to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.13,0:08:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN coughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.97,0:08:24.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Patty, Carne, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.54,0:08:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.54,0:08:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY]\NAll right already!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARNE]\NMe too? All right, I'm comin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.96,0:08:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha! It's no use.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.92,0:08:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He's going to die\Nwithin the hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NDon't you dare die, Ghin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.92,0:08:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.75,0:08:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.84,0:08:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] You can't let\Nsomeone like him win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Stick around. Now, I'm mad!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll wanna see what I'm\Ngoing to do to him next!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:57.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN grunting]\NYou can't defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.29,0:08:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.00,0:09:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Attacking him head on\Nis exactly what he wants!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.21,0:09:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He's strongest that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.87,0:09:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.25,0:09:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Go ahead and\Ngive it your best shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NDon't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.13,0:09:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dumb kid. When you lose your\Npatience, you become easy prey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.75,0:09:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You are only running toward\None thing, Chore Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.67,0:09:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,And that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.46,0:09:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,He's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.09,0:09:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Really dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.17,0:09:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,... your funeral.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.63,0:09:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NMy funeral?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.59,0:09:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, get out of there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.29,0:09:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,He got hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.30,0:09:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.59,0:09:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Poor guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NHuh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.13,0:09:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NGum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.42,0:09:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh... C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.72,0:09:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The spikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.42,0:09:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.12,0:09:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NJust try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.17,0:09:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got no place to hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.88,0:10:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\N... Pistol!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.26,0:10:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.05,0:10:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.30,0:10:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.72,0:10:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES chattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:36.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE Z]\NDon Krieg is down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.50,0:10:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That punk got him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.04,0:10:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE J]\NWhat is that kid, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.17,0:10:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,He punched him right\Nthrough the spikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.25,0:10:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE Z]\NThat's messed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.09,0:10:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE J]\NI've never seen him get hit
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.59,0:10:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,in any kind of fight, ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.97,0:10:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE A] He busted right\Nthrough that porcupine cape
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.33,0:10:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and smashed him\Nright in the face!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:11:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE Z]\NI... I can't believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.38,0:11:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]\NSo, is this my funeral?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.09,0:11:13.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Or yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.30,0:11:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't kill me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]\N...with little spikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.21,0:11:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,My funeral...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.38,0:11:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]\N...will take more than this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.71,0:11:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY pants]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.09,0:11:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] You'll have to\Ndo better than that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.92,0:11:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...if you wanna beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.00,0:11:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I don't think its\Ntime for me to die, just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.01,0:12:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I know one thing, he's nuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.63,0:12:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I've seen one or\Ntwo like him before.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.01,0:12:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Stubborn kids who'd rather die,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.79,0:12:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,than have to turn away from\Na fight, once it's started.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.05,0:12:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.67,0:12:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.17,0:12:34.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad he's with us,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,'cause guys like that\Nare hell to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.59,0:12:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] I don't care\Nif he wins or loses,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.55,0:12:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I consider it an honor,\Njust to be able to watch him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.80,0:12:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.21,0:13:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY]\NHey, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.04,0:13:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[CARNE]\NYou all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.34,0:13:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Try to breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You need a little fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.34,0:13:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You want a pillow\Nor maybe some water?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.59,0:13:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.75,0:13:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[labored breathing]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.38,0:13:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.55,0:13:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.30,0:13:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I make a great banana pudding.\NWant some?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.42,0:13:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot, we don't want\Nhim to choke to death
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.50,0:13:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,on any of your\Nculinary disasters!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.92,0:13:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Better that, than\Nthe trots he'd get
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,from choking down one of\Nyour raunchy meat pies!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I won't feed\Nhim one of my meat pies,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.67,0:13:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,is because after one bite,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,he'd think he'd died\Nand gone to heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.63,0:13:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.46,0:13:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't die yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.09,0:13:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, breathe more!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not really dead,\Nyou're not really dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.55,0:14:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not really dead,\Nyou're not really dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.51,0:14:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you're not really dead,\Nyou're not really dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.58,0:14:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.63,0:14:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[coughs, pants]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.96,0:14:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[BOTH]\NHe's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[GHIN]\NDon... Don... Don Krieg.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.21,0:14:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.29,0:14:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that was just luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.79,0:14:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don Krieg is gonna get up and\Nkick his ass any minute now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.17,0:14:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Just watch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.59,0:14:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.59,0:14:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:41.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.09,0:14:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not your funeral,\Nyet, is it? Too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NBecause one of us has gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.76,0:14:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And since I'm here...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd really like to\Npay my respects!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.13,0:15:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.97,0:15:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NYou first!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.84,0:15:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG groans]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.38,0:15:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE Z]\NThis can't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,He's taken another fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.58,0:15:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But... But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen anyone hit him,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.67,0:15:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,because their usually dead\Nbefore they get close enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.63,0:15:26.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact is... He might\Nnot actually be invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.08,0:15:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[gulps]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.09,0:15:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE B]\NWhat the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.59,0:15:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The kid's pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, no kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.92,0:15:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Finish him off, chore boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.71,0:15:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! End it once and for all!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.88,0:15:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,That punk is fighting\Nwith Don Krieg
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.71,0:15:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,as if he were the same strength!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.34,0:16:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This can't be real. It's like\NI'm watching my own nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,He's supposed to\Nbe truly invincible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.38,0:16:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,If he get's beaten by this\Nlittle kid, his reputation
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.67,0:16:05.42,Default,,0,0,0,,will be completely--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up, maggots!\NNever doubt me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.13,0:16:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.50,0:16:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.96,0:16:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES]\NHa, ha!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.67,0:16:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:18.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What... was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.84,0:16:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE B] Finally, he's\Ngonna stop messing around
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.97,0:16:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,and step up his game.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.76,0:16:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE C]\NThe Mighty Battle Spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that?\NAn exploding spear?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.50,0:16:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.42,0:16:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You gonna try\Nto hide from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.47,0:16:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.75,0:16:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,This should be fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.75,0:16:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My Mighty Battle Spear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.50,0:16:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's different from the one\NI was fighting with earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.34,0:16:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,When this thing hits you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.38,0:16:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,you won't just be\Nwounded and flailing,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.79,0:16:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,you will be blown\Nstraight into Hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.09,0:16:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.92,0:16:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.63,0:16:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not a normal spear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.05,0:16:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY] Woah, woah,\Nwoah, not in the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.33,0:16:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Not in the water! [grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.75,0:16:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That spear really sucks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.21,0:17:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It explodes every time\Nhe hits anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.34,0:17:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]\NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.51,0:17:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,My knees...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:08.80,Default,,0,0,0,,He's lost way too much blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.80,0:17:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He can't fight for much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.01,0:17:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,This better end quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.97,0:17:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You look tired, too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.08,0:17:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess you should've saved\Na little more energy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.75,0:17:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NDamn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.71,0:17:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,With everything rocking,\NI can't hit him with full force.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.50,0:17:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never in my life seen\Na more stunning weapon
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.88,0:17:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,than The Mighty Battle Spear.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.84,0:17:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Don Krieg is the only one strong\Nenough to handle the spear,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.76,0:17:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,since the harder\Nhe strikes with it,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.42,0:17:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,the bigger the\Nexplosion it causes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.33,0:17:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyone else would just\Nbe completely destroyed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.50,0:17:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,by their own pathetic attempt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.84,0:17:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,--[KRIEG yells]\N--[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.96,0:17:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG, LUFFY grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:46.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's strength...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,His strength is the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.59,0:17:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He causes the kind of\Ndamage no one else can
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.01,0:17:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,'cause there's just no one\Nelse who can swing a spear
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.13,0:17:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that easily weighs\Nmore than a ton.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.63,0:17:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATE J]\NThat's exactly why Don Kreig
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.46,0:17:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,is the most dangerous\Nman in the East Blue!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:04.62,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG, LUFFY grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.62,0:18:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yelping]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.96,0:18:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.96,0:18:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.97,0:18:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY, KRIEG grunt]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.29,0:18:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Chore boy, look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,[PATTY, CARNE gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.25,0:18:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew... that was really close.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.55,0:18:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.92,0:18:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NYou're just like a little bug!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.33,0:18:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yelping]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.62,0:18:35.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.63,0:18:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Chore Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.55,0:18:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.00,0:18:47.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NHeh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.00,0:18:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.50,0:18:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,That's rough.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.96,0:18:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You all right, Chore Boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.71,0:19:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG] Heh. I'm not\Nfinished with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.09,0:19:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If you hadn't made me so angry,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have killed\Nyou more quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.25,0:19:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,[laughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.33,0:19:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no way that Chore Boy\Ncan take much more of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.96,0:19:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That spear is way too powerful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.84,0:19:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.80,0:19:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with a hundred\Nthousand more weapons,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.58,0:19:28.21,Default,,0,0,0,,our Chore boy can still\Nbring him to his knees,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.21,0:19:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,because he does not know fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.34,0:19:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.12,0:19:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps, grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.00,0:19:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[PIRATES chuckle]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.30,0:19:42.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.29,0:19:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NHeh. That was too easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.59,0:19:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.92,0:19:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NHuh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.63,0:20:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.21,0:20:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NHeh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, that's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Stand or fall...\NLife or death...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,In a struggle for\Nyour very existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,you cannot have even the\Nslightest bit of fear,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.08,0:20:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,or you will be lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.09,0:20:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.55,0:20:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,That kid out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.46,0:20:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG, LUFFY yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,When he's fighting...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.75,0:20:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF]\NHe's not afraid of anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.17,0:20:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even death!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.71,0:20:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.17,0:20:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY yelling]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.04,0:21:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY groaning]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.63,0:21:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it just instinct,\Nor all a plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.71,0:21:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll know soon, if he lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.59,0:21:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.17,0:21:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NWhat plan? Killing himself?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.00,0:21:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You... son of a bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.00,0:21:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NHeh!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.79,0:21:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOKS cheering]
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,[COOK J]\NWay to go Chore Boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.04,0:21:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,--[COOK K] Do it again!\N--[COOK L] Kick his ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.59,0:21:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, today\Nis your funeral!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.17,0:21:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I am invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.71,0:22:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There is no doubt that Krieg\Nand his pirates are strong,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.25,0:22:11.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But Chore Boy has something\Nthey'll never have.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.25,0:22:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[ZEFF] Krieg may have more\Npirates at his command
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.84,0:22:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,than anyone else before him,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.42,0:22:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,he may have terrible weapons\Nthat cause mass destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.17,0:22:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,to everything in his path,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.92,0:22:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but he will never\Nhave that kid's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.87,0:22:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.05,0:22:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.59,0:22:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG]\NHuh? What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.05,0:22:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,My Battle Spear!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.37,0:22:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell did you do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.62,0:22:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I just punched it in\Nthe head five times.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.84,0:22:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks tired,\Nmaybe it needs a rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.84,0:23:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,[KRIEG growling]
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.13,0:23:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NNow, it's my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.34,0:23:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As a kid, I never stopped{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.72,0:23:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Searching for a great treasure{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.33,0:23:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had a map in my mind{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.09,0:23:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That I knew would lead me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.22,0:23:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I had to find my way{\i0}\N{\i1}to that place{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.92,0:23:30.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Before someone could beat me{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.42,0:23:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The promised land{\i0}\N{\i1}was in my grasp{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.04,0:23:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And I wouldn't let go{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.13,0:23:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My only dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.04,0:23:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I won't stop chasing it{\i0}\N{\i1}until it comes true{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.67,0:23:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if the world ever changes{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.96,0:23:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll call out your name{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.80,0:24:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We could return to the time{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.84,0:24:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}When everything's the same{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.79,0:24:09.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As long as I'm with you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.05,0:24:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My memories won't fade{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.92,0:24:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Waiting for that{\i0}\N{\i1}one true dream...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.83,0:24:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NWhy does he keep fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.92,0:24:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he trying to\Nget himself killed?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.30,0:24:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No, he's not even scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.30,0:24:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long\Ntime since I fought
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.17,0:24:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,like I had something\Nworth dying for.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.38,0:24:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NThis is it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.80,0:24:40.34,Default,,0,0,0,,[SANJI]\NChore Boy, Don't die like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.34,0:24:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,[LUFFY]\NOn the next One Piece,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.01,0:24:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,"The Conclusion of\Nthe Deadly Battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:44.08,0:24:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A Spear of Blind Determination!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.50,0:24:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be\NKing of the Pirates!

